Anthony Hayes (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anthony_Hayes_(actor) 0 Anthony Hayes (born 21 September 1977) is an Australian actor, best known for his roles in War Machine, The Light Between Oceans, The Slap, Look Both Ways, The Boys, Rabbit-Proof Fence, Animal Kingdom and soap opera Paradise Beach.
